==English==
===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ˈblez.ɑɹ/  ([[Rhymes:English:-ɒɹ|rhymes]])

===Noun===
'''blazar''' (''plural'' '''blazars''')

# {{astronomy}} A highly [[variable]] active [[galaxy]], characterized by a very [[compact]] and highly variable energy source at the center and its strong [[optical]] [[polarization]] and [[variability]].
# {{astronomy}} Collectively, optically violent [[variable]]s and [[BL Lac object]]s.

